## 自定义规则配置

在 `config/xp_ai_coding_config.yaml` 中添加：

```yaml
standards_config:
  rule_sets:
    xiaopeng_specific:
      enabled: true
      custom_rules:
        - id: xp_custom_naming
          name: "小鹏自定义命名规范"
          pattern: "^XP[A-Z][a-zA-Z0-9]*$"
          severity: error
          file_patterns: ["**/*.h"]

        - id: xp_no_hardcoded_url
          name: "禁止硬编码API地址"
          pattern: "https?://[a-zA-Z0-9./]+"
          severity: warning
          file_patterns: ["**/*.swift", "**/*.m"]

        - id: xp_log_format
          name: "日志格式规范"
          description: "使用XPLogger而非NSLog/print"
          severity: info
          file_patterns: ["**/*.m", "**/*.swift"]
```
